<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title>Portable Charger | Project Details</title>
    <style>
        /* 1. Custom Slate Grey Overrides for this page only */
        :root {
            --slate-grey: #708090;
            --slate-hover: #8494a5;
        }

        /* 2. Make buttons fill the "pages" better */
        .project-step {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 5%;
            /* Uses the snap height from your style.css */
        }

        form {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1000px;
        }

        .content-box-button {
        display: block;
        background: var(--slate-grey);
        color: white;
        /* ADD THE BORDER BELOW */
        border: 2px solid #3b82f6; 
        text-align: center;
        padding: 80px 40px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-radius: 20px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

        .content-box-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            background: var(--slate-hover);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .content-box-button h1 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        /* ADD THESE THREE LINES */
        display: inline-block;
        border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); 
        padding-bottom: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content-box-button p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 15px auto 0;
        }

        /* 3. Fixed Footer for Contact Info */
        .contact-footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.95); /* Matches your --card-bg */
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--slate-grey);
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .contact-info {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Using your existing .btn class from style.css but ensuring it fits the footer */
        .contact-footer .btn {
            padding: 8px 25px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }
        /* Optional: Make the border glow brighter on hover */
        .content-box-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            background: var(--slate-hover);
            border-color: #60a5fa; 
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
        }
        
        .centered-title {
            margin-top: 40px !important;
        }
        .btn-back-home {
    /* Changed to fixed so it stays visible while scrolling through sections */
    position: fixed; 
    top: 25px; /* Slightly higher to sit neatly inside the 12px border */
    left: 25px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: rgba(11, 18, 33, 0.8); /* Darker background to pop against images */
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    z-index: 10001; /* High z-index to stay above everything */
}

.btn-back-home:hover {
    color: #ffffff;
    border-color: #3b82f6;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="scroll-wrapper">

        <section class="project-step">
            <form action="/views/portable-charger-vision.ejs" method="get">
                <button class="content-box-button" type="submit">
                    <h1>Goals</h1>
                    <p>Framework of Project Details and Growth Experiences. Included are the Challenges faced throughout the project and Final Outcomes.</p>
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section class="project-step">
            <form action="/views/portable-charger-pcb.ejs" method="get">
                <button class="content-box-button" type="submit">
                    <h1>PCB Design</h1>
                    <p>Custom 18650 Battery Holder to Safely Distribute the Voltage from a TP4056 Breakout Board to a Buck Boost Converter and Finally to an iPhone.</p>
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section class="project-step">
            <form action="/views/portable-charger-cad.ejs" method="get">
                <button class="content-box-button" type="submit">
                    <h1>Fusion CAD Design</h1>
                    <p>Optimizing Space and Thermal Constraints to fit a Portable Charger.</p>
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section class="project-step">
            <form action="/portable-charger/final-build" method="get">
                <button class="content-box-button" type="submit">
                    <h1>Final Build</h1>
                    <p>Finished Project with All Components Integrated and Tested.</p>
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

    </div>

    <footer class="contact-footer">
        <div class="contact-info">
            <strong>Phone:</strong> (859) 608-3061 | 
            <strong>Email:</strong> <em>m1287666@moreheadstate.edu</em>
        </div>
        <a href="index.ejs" class="btn-back-home">Back to Home</a>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>